description: This action removes a tag from an Amazon FSx resource.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: The ARN of the Amazon FSx resource to untag.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A list of keys of tags on the resource to untag. In case the tag key doesn't exist, the call will still succeed to be idempotent. (string) --- A string of 1 to 128 characters that specifies the key for a tag. Tag keys must be unique for the resource to which they are attached.
